text: Víctor Andrés Donoso Andalaft (born 27 November 1990) is a Chilean handball player for KH Kopřivnice in the czech Strabag Rail extraliga and the Chilean national team.EHF profile2019 World Men's Handball Championship roster He participated at the 2017 World Men's Handball Championship.2017 World Championship roster ==References== Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Santiago Category:Chilean male handball players Category:Expatriate handball players Category:Chilean expatriate sportspeople in France Category:Chilean expatriate sportspeople in Italy Category:Chilean expatriate sportspeople in Slovakia Category:Pan American Games medalists in handball Category:Pan American Games silver medalists for Chile Category:Handball players at the 2019 Pan American Games
